{"tid":934790,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"🎄[港大精算偷拍犯聖誕特輯2] 祺　感化還好嗎　尚愛拍少女裸體嗎🎄","createTime":"2018-12-09T14:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T14:07:18.000Z","uid":161050,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3706ce472d6330f7f8c33813f52ab9457db4e838","tid":934790,"uid":161050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">祺　感化</span>還好嗎　尚愛<span style=\"color: red;\">拍少女裸體嗎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近　近乎沒露面　你有新對象嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n＊真想<span style=\"color: red;\">你帶我見</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">你剛識到的她</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　我想聽你意見　這算是病吧<br />\n　為何無論你　願意怎樣試<br />\n　怎樣也不可抗拒去<span style=\"color: red;\">偷拍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (怎樣也沒令自己<span style=\"color: red;\">唔偷拍</span>)<br />\n<br />\n＃難道沒<span style=\"color: red;\">打J</span>太耐　<span style=\"color: red;\">精子都谷上腦袋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　試圖<span style=\"color: red;\">搵女朋友</span>　也顯得不自在<br />\n　不懂得如何談戀愛　還是<span style=\"color: red;\">你太淫賤</span>　對<span style=\"color: red;\">祼體</span>太放不開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n△難道是<span style=\"color: red;\">壓抑</span>太耐　<span style=\"color: red;\">忍唔住要去偷拍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">自己</span>也<span style=\"color: red;\">入鏡</span>了　留在<span style=\"color: red;\">證據</span>所在<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">部cam</span>　放滿你的<span style=\"color: red;\">影片</span>　難怪<span style=\"color: red;\">你已經</span>　再沒<span style=\"color: red;\">睇AV</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">祺</span>　有時仍很怕　<span style=\"color: red;\">重做到精算師嗎</span><br />\n往事若然未落幕　再揭起有害嗎<br />\n<br />\nRepeat (＊),＃,△<br />\n<br />\n難道<span style=\"color: red;\">耶穌玩鳩你　點解會俾人捉到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試圖<span style=\"color: red;\">搵返條女</span>　也<span style=\"color: red;\">俾女朋友飛</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好彩屋企背景良好　又係名校出身　判感化十八個月</span><br />\n<br />\n難道<span style=\"color: red;\">得罪人太多　連登</span>的<span style=\"color: red;\">post 俾人推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n往事卻似斷箭　還剩下在體內<br />\n若<span style=\"color: red;\">連登</span>　放滿<span style=\"color: red;\">了你的post</span>　害怕<span style=\"color: red;\">以後也</span>　再沒法<span style=\"color: red;\">搵工</span>　[/quote]<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BXGASF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BXGASF.jpg&h=2a44a14e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a60df04d4b63bc4d5b9aadbccf95ca2551b5ad18","tid":934790,"uid":20066,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201